NoUI DERP POC

**DERP Knowledge Analysis & Verification Report**

Complete RMC Verification Including SS Make-Up, Disability, and
DROP/DROP II

Date: February 21, 2026 \| Version: 3.0 \| Source: DRMC Jan 2024 Edition

1\. Executive Summary

We have obtained and fully analyzed the complete Denver Revised
Municipal Code (DRMC), Sections 18-391 through 18-430.7, January 2024
edition. This 61-page document is the ultimate governing authority for
all DERP benefit provisions, covering Division 1 (Generally), Division 2
(1963 Retirement Plan), Division 3 (DROP), and Division 4 (DROP II).

This version expands our analysis to include all benefit types
documented in the RMC, including provisions currently out of scope for
the POC (Social Security Make-Up, Disability Retirement, DROP, and DROP
II). While these will not be implemented in the initial POC, having the
complete statutory analysis documented now means we can expand scope
with confidence and without re-analysis.

  -------------------------- ----------- ---------------------------------
